GTK ALSA audio mixer gamix by Fumihiko Murata <fmurata@p1.tcnet.ne.jp>
                              Daimon Software

This is a mixer application for ALSA which usined GTK.

FEATURES:
 * edit all mixer elements / mixer switches
 * edit mixer list
 * auto unmute for displyed mixer elements
 * supported language: Japanese German

<Usage>
  gamix [options]
  [options]
    -c [finename]
      change gamix configuration file.
      If filename is not start from '/',file is in $HOME/.gamix/ directory.

